  PDF file format. If you are using the correct file type\, below are some 
 additional troubleshooting suggestions:</span></span></span></span></span>
 </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Verify that a Scoring Guide is selected before scanning\; 
 otherwise\, the scan won’t run.</li>\n<li>Upload a text-based PDF (not a
 n image-only PDF).&nbsp\;</li>\n<li>Use Chrome or Edge\; try an incognito 
 window\; close extra Big Interview tabs\; refresh ResumeAI and re-upload i
 f “Scanning…” lasts &gt\;3–5 minutes.</li>\n<li>Avoid VPNs or aggr
 essive ad/script blockers\; temporarily disable extensions and try a diffe
 rent network if possible.</li>\n<li><span class="cc-v6b8k"><span class="cc
 -1ab24 cc-sp3ed"><span class="cc-iw847 cc-1plpv cc-rzz1b cc-1o31k cc-bxbnb
 "><span class="cc-1p1u8"><span class="cc-1yk1e cc-oao3j">If you continue t
