DESCRIPTION:[BSAD222 Banner - June 2017.png] (https://canvas.unl.edu/course
 s/208826/files/23678536/preview)\n\nTo successfully pass BSAD 222\, you mu
 st attend all in-person classes. We do understand\, however\, that circums
 tances may occur in which you miss a class session. In this situation\, we
  want to provide you with an opportunity to complete an alternative assign
 ment to showcase that you have reviewed the material from the module you m
 issed\, understand it\, and demonstrate your knowledge of the topic to aid
  you in your career development and planning.\n\nAfter communicating with 
 your lead section instructor regarding the material you missed\, you may b
 e granted a one-time exception to complete an alternative assignment. To m
 ake up for your missed attendance\, you must complete the make-up assignme
 nt at the link below and submit the PDF by the deadline issued in order to
  return to good standing in the course. \n\nSince this is a condensed cou
 rse with a limited number of class meetings\, please understand that any a
 dditional absence will result in a “No Pass” for the course. If you a
 re having any difficulties\, you are encouraged to proactively reach out t
 o your lead section instructor to create a plan for success.\n\n[Make-up A
 ssignment Link (Qualtrics Form)] (https://unlcba.az1.qualtrics.com/jfe/for
 m/SV_6gn8LUGowUAyPDE)
