 8536/preview" alt="BSAD222 Banner - June 2017.png" width="3333" height="41
 7" data-api-endpoint="https://canvas.unl.edu/api/v1/courses/208826/files/2
 3678536" data-api-returntype="File" loading="lazy"></p>\n<p>To successfull
 y pass BSAD 222\, you must attend all in-person classes. We do understand\
 , however\, that circumstances may occur in which you miss a class session
 . In this situation\, we want to provide you with an opportunity to comple
 te an alternative assignment to showcase that you have reviewed the materi
 al from the module you missed\, understand it\, and demonstrate your knowl
 edge of the topic to aid you in your career development and planning.</p>\
