 con-content" style="display: none\;">&nbsp\;</span></i> Overview</h3>\n<p>
 CliftonStrengths for Students is a personalized talent assessment that sho
 wcases each individual’s top five themes of talent. Understanding your t
 op five themes of talent will allow you to build a professional brand and 
 communicate your unique abilities to employers in a clear and memorable ma
 nner. <strong>This assignment is designed for you to:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n
 <li>Identify your natural talents so you can begin to practice them and ho
 ne them into Strengths</li>\n<li>Understand your CliftonStrengths results 
 and the role they play in worker engagement</li>\n<li>Begin to consider th
 e impact that your Strengths have upon how you make decisions and plans</l
 i>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Submission Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>Submit you
 r CliftonStrengths Top 5 Report or CliftonStrengths for Students to Canvas
  by downloading it from the <a class="inline_disabled" href="https://www.s
 trengthsquest.com/home.aspx" target="_blank">CliftonStrengths for Students
  website</a>. Review the detailed instructions below to see how to access 
 your results if you have previously taken the assessment or how to redeem 
 the access code that will be emailed to you if you have not taken the asse
 ssment before.</p>\n<div class=" dp-callout-color-lt-danger dp-callout car
