  language.\n<ul>\n<li><em>Note: international students are encouraged to s
 elect their native language</em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Select "Take the 
 CliftonStrengths assessment" and read the directions carefully.</li>\n<li>
 Finalize your demographic information.</li>\n<li>Take the assessment. If y
 ou lose your internet connection\, you will be able to sign back in and be
