  you might want to do?<br>\n<ul>\n<li><em>Alternatively\, if you are uncer
 tain about your career goals\, what is making you feel stuck? Why?<br></em
 ></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Action Item:</strong> What is one thing 
 that you could do in the next 3 months to feel more confident in your care
 er selection?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp\;</p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 14pt
 \;"><i class="icon-reply-2 icon-Solid" aria-hidden="true"><span class="dp-
 icon-content" style="display: none\;">&nbsp\;</span></i><strong>&nbsp\;</s
 trong><span style="text-decoration: underline\;"><strong>Review Peer Posts
 </strong></span></span></p>\n<ul style="list-style-type: disc\;">\n<li>Rev
 iew 2-3 of your peers reflections to gain additional ideas for career expl
 oration or consideration.</li>\n<li>You may be asked to reflect on your va
 lues and career selections with your peers in class\, so you'll want to ha
 ve reviewed a few for richer discussion.&nbsp\;</li>\n<li><strong>No peer 
 replies are required</strong>\, but you're welcome to leave a comment if y
 ou like or want to connect with a peer that has similar interests.&nbsp\;<
 /li>\n</ul>\n</div><script src="https://instructure-uploads.s3.amazonaws.c
 om/account_65070000000000001/attachments/21770614/dp_app.js"></script>
END:VEVENT
