 get="_blank">Handshake profile</a> showing:</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li style="
 list-style-type: none\;">\n<ul style="list-style-type: disc\;">\n<li>Profe
 ssional headshot.</li>\n<li>Looking for: Types of roles\, industries\, and
