 ack</h3>\n<p><strong>Grading:&nbsp\;</strong> <br>You will be graded on th
 e following scale:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong data-start="556" data-end="569
 ">Complete: </strong>Your submitted PDF includes all required sections and
  demonstrates thoughtful engagement with the Career Growth Strategy and Ac
 tion Plan. Your action steps and reflections are realistic\, specific\, an
 d clearly connected to your interests\, strengths\, and values.</li>\n<li>
 \n<strong>Incomplete: </strong>Your submission is missing one or more requ
 ired components\, does not meet the minimum character requirements\, or la
 cks sufficient detail to demonstrate meaningful engagement. <span style="b
 ackground-color: #fbeeb8\;">You will be asked to revise and resubmit withi
 n the timeline provided by your moderator.&nbsp\;</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</
 div>\n<div id="kl_custom_block_4" class="">\n<h3>\n<i class="far fa-questi
 on-circle" aria-hidden="true"><span class="dp-icon-content" style="display
 : none\;">&nbsp\;</span></i>FAQs</h3>\n<p><strong>How long will this take?
 </strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Plan for at least 30 minutes. Many questions incl
 ude reflection and minimum character requirements\, so give yourself unint
 errupted time.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Can I leave and come back later?</s
 trong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Yes\, as long as you use the same device/browser and
  do not clear your cache. It’s recommended that you complete the assignm
 ent in one sitting if possible.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Why can’t I move
  forward?</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Some questions require a minimum number 
 of selections\, a minimum character count\, and/or all required fields to 
 be completed. Make sure you’ve met all instructions before moving to the
  next page.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What if I’m unsure about my career p
 ath?</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>That’s completely normal. This assignment i
 s designed to help you explore possibilities\, not commit to a final decis
 ion.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What if I have technical issues?</strong></p>
 \n<ul>\n<li>Take a screenshot and contact your moderator as soon as possib
 le.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><script src="https://instructure-up
 loads.s3.amazonaws.com/account_65070000000000001/attachments/21770614/dp_a
 pp.js"></script>
END:VEVENT
