 he day of your appointment\, you may use Student Success Hub or call 402-4
 72-7272 to reschedule your appointment. You are also expected to contact y
 our assigned coach directly via Canvas messages to let them know what is g
 oing on as soon as possible.<strong></strong>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div
 >\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="dp-content-block kl_custom_block_3">\n<h3 c
 lass="dp-has-icon">\n<i class="fas fa-share-square" aria-hidden="true"><sp
 an class="dp-icon-content" style="display: none\;">&nbsp\;</span></i> Grad
 ing and Feedback</h3>\n<p><strong>Grading:&nbsp\;</strong> <br>You will re
 ceive either a "Complete" or an "Incomplete" for this assignment based on 
 whether you attend your 1:1 coaching session.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="
 background-color: #fbeeb8\;"><strong>If you schedule and then fail to show
  up for 2 appointments without proactively communicating with your assigne
 d coach\, you will receive a "No Pass".</strong></span></li>\n<li><span st
 yle="background-color: #fbeeb8\;"><strong>If you do not complete your coac
 hing session by the assigned due date\, you will receive a "No Pass" for t
 he course.</strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class="dp-content-blo
 ck kl_custom_block_4">\n<h3 class="dp-has-icon">\n<i class="far fa-questio
