 lay the three variables in different colors\, your predicted temperature (
 green)\, the actual temperature (red)\, and the historic temperature (blue
 ) from 1981.</p>\n<p>Make your graph easy to read:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Make a t
 itle</li>\n<li>Label your axes</li>\n<li>Use other design tools as you ple
