DESCRIPTION:**************************************************************\
 nGEOG 155 Minor Assignment: attend a relevant lecture on campus\n*********
 *****************************************************\n\n---------\n25 poi
 nts\n---------\n\n------------\nDue: 12/1/25\n------------\n\n------------
 -\nInstructions:\n-------------\n\nFind a free and open lecture on campus 
 and attend the lecture. The lecture must be related to Physical Geography 
 in some way. In-person attendance for a lecture is required\, except with 
 permission from the instructor.\n\nPlaces to look for lectures on campus:\
 n\n [https://events.unl.edu] (https://events.unl.edu/)\n\n https://resea
 rch.unl.edu/nebraskalectures/\n\n[https://enthompson.unl.edu] (https://ent
 hompson.unl.edu/)\n\nhttps://cas.unl.edu/academics/cas-inquire/\n\n-------
 ---------\nWhat to turn in:\n----------------\n\nA Microsoft word document
  uploaded to Canvas with your name\, date\, and class listed\, answering t
 hese questions:\n\n* What lecture did you attend and why?\n\n* How is it r
 elevant to GEOG 155?\n\n* Did you enjoy the lecture – be honest!\n\nAnsw
 ers should be written in short\, complete sentences. Total writing should 
 be no longer than 100 words.\n\nHow you’ll be graded: 15 points for atte
 nding the lecture. 10 points on the quality of writing and clarity of your
  answers.
