 ampus</h1>\n<h2>25 points</h2>\n<h2>Due: 12/1/25</h2>\n<h2>Instructions:</
 h2>\n<p>Find a free and open lecture on campus and attend the lecture. The
  lecture must be related to Physical Geography in some way. <em><u>In-pers
 on attendance for a lecture is required\, except with permission from the 
