 p><span>&nbsp\;</span><a href="https://events.unl.edu/">https://events.unl
 .edu</a></p>\n<p><span>&nbsp\;</span><a href="https://research.unl.edu/neb
 raskalectures/">https://research.unl.edu/nebraskalectures/</a></p>\n<p><a 
 href="https://enthompson.unl.edu/">https://enthompson.unl.edu</a></p>\n<p>
 <a href="https://cas.unl.edu/academics/cas-inquire/">https://cas.unl.edu/a
 cademics/cas-inquire/</a></p>\n<h2>What to turn in:</h2>\n<p>A Microsoft w
 ord document uploaded to Canvas with your name\, date\, and class listed\,
