  why?</li>\n<li>How is it relevant to GEOG 155?</li>\n<li>Did you enjoy th
 e lecture – be honest!</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Answers should be written
  in short\, complete sentences. Total writing should be no longer than 100
  words.</strong></p>\n<p>How you’ll be graded: 15 points for attending t
 he lecture. 10 points on the quality of writing and clarity of your answer
 s.</p><script src="https://instructure-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/account_65
 070000000000001/attachments/21770614/dp_app.js"></script>
